(d) A rule adopted under this section is not effective until the rule is filed with the secretary of state.

(e) A rule adopted by the Texas Lottery Commission under Subsection (a) may exempt from the requirements of Section 721.002 (Inscription Required on State-owned Motor Vehicles) only a motor vehicle used exclusively for surveillance purposes.

*Acts 2021, 87th Leg., R.S., Ch. 303 (S.B.795), Sec. 1, eff. September 1, 2021.*
